Brian Baldwin
Back To Team













Senior Analyst & PartnerBrian Baldwin is a Partner and Senior Analyst and has been a member of the Investment Team of Trian since August 2007. As of September 2015, Mr. Baldwin attends of the Board of Directors and the Compensation Committee of Pentair plc in a non-voting, non-participating observer capacity. Prior to joining Trian, he was an analyst at Merrill Lynch Global Private Equity from July 2005 to July 2007.
Mr. Baldwin received a B.S., summa cum laude, from The Wharton School at the University of Pennsylvania.



