* Trian Advisory Partners, while not employees of Trian, are experienced business leaders and investment professionals who assist Trian with various aspects of its investment process. The affiliations listed in the Advisory Partner bios are included for identification purposes only.
In October 2015, Trian’s Legal Team was named by The Legal 500 (GC Powerlist) as one of the most influential and innovative in-house legal teams in the United States alongside teams from major corporations, including: American Express, GE, AT&T, Bristol Myers-Squibb, Google, Johnson & Johnson, Kellogg’s, JP Morgan, Microsoft, Nike, PepsiCo, Shell, Starbucks and Wendy’s.














